description: Freemelt Holding AB (publ) is a SE-based company operating in  industry. The company is headquartered in Stockholm, Stockholm. The company went IPO on 2021-07-07. Freemelt Holding AB (publ) is a Sweden-based high-tech growth company, which creates new opportunities for rapid growth in 3D printing, also known as additive manufacturing. The firm was founded in 2017 and develops a new patent-pending technology in electron beam technology and launched Freemelt ONE, which is a 3D printer optimized for professional development of new metal materials.
